{"tid":1255494,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"多倫多大學specialist定double major?","createTime":"2019-06-24T13:50:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T14:15:59.000Z","uid":238755,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"be051d54dc18fc5718101fc099584e2d191d8a76","tid":1255494,"uid":238755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T13:50:22.000Z","msg":"我依加係UTSG life sciences year 1，唔知揀邊樣好 (Specialist psychology/ double major psychology + criminology)，諗住之後再係加拿大/英國/香港讀master。<br />\n<br />\nSpecialist夠專，識到多啲prof幫手寫推薦信入master，剩低可以揀bird courses。但怕深得濟會拉低GPA入唔到master/競爭力太大，同埋唔中意上seminar。<br />\n<br />\nDouble major出路廣啲，邊樣唔掂都有個拉住，同埋兩科都幾有興趣。但之後3年都完全真係讀呢啲，冇bird courses同CR，同怕master啲人見我double major而唔揀我先。<br />\n<br />\n應該揀邊個好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b529a239743bdf5d2b8b6980b1c826de6e5d0efa","tid":1255494,"uid":57378,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T15:44:07.000Z","msg":"讀碩士點解要推薦信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e18c11460368ff72c7a14c4e0fe33f066d21f67","tid":1255494,"uid":238755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b529a239743bdf5d2b8b6980b1c826de6e5d0efa","tid":1255494,"uid":57378,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T15:44:07.000Z","msg":"讀碩士點解要推薦信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T15:58:30.000Z","msg":"加拿大讀master既話最好有"},{"pid":"ccd721855a9fe8b0c38bbcc414f71b0e065948fe","tid":1255494,"uid":144324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T10:49:41.000Z","msg":"Double major <br />\n利申 applied stat specialist <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/